      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is a well-sorted E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example utilizes the Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox for maximum engagement. Critically, the rear subframe has been reinforced and the double-VANOS system has been overhauled to ensure optimal cam timing and reliability. The chassis maintains its composure through a limited-slip differential and refreshed suspension geometry. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical synchronization and compression across all cylinders remain within tight tolerances. It is a mechanically robust specimen of BMW's analog era, offering exceptional turn-in response and a linear power band.",
