    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This chassis benefits from a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. Key preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including documented rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul to ensure optimal cam phasing. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, providing the tactile feedback and balanced turn-in expected of this platform. While the aesthetic reflects its status as a well-loved driver's car, the drivetrain remains robust and free of parasitic loss, making it an ideal candidate for an enthusiast seeking performance over concours perfection.",
